{{link-fr|药用当归|Angélique officinale}}是当地的特色农产品<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.france-pittoresque.com/spip.php?rubrique161|title=Patrimoine : Gastronomie|accessdate=2019-12-12|author=france-pittoresque.com|language=fr|publisher=france-pittoresque.com|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417201257/https://www.france-pittoresque.com/spip.php?rubrique161|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

